data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Jasper, Alabama! This updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom would be great for any family! The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated with modern appliances, stylish countertops, and plenty of storage! Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area is ideal for family meals or entertaining guests.
The three bedrooms offer flexibility for families or those in need of a home office. This home also includes a bonus room with a wood-burning fireplace which adds versatility, whether you envision a home gym, playroom, or office space. One of the highlights of this property is the fenced backyard with plenty of space for animals or outdoor activities! Conveniently located in Jasper, you'll have easy access to local restaurants, schools, and everything Jasper has to offer! Don't miss the chance to make this 3/2 residence your own – Call your favorite realtor and schedule a showing today!
